    "subject": "Riflegrenade disappears of the gun when you get revived",
    "description": "The title doesn't explain everything but I explain here how to reproduce this bug:\r\n\r\nFirst you put the riflegrenade on your K43/M1 Garand. Then you get killed and then revived. You still have your riflegrenade when you get revived. But the thing is when you switch weapon to any other weapon and then take back your K43/M1 Garand, the riflegrenade has disappeared.\r\n\r\nWhen you have your riflegrenade on and you switch your weapons to another one and then back, it won't take away your riflegrenade out of the gun.\r\n\r\n-*S",
